                        <interp inst="t18350615-name-1050" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS ARKELL</persName>
                  </hi>. The prisoner came to my master's shop, on the 3rd of June—he said he came from Mrs. Bardell's—I took him there, but I</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183506150161"></xptr>
               <p>knew nothing of the other charge—I took him back to my master, and Mr. Wright came in and accused him of this.</p>
